wiki.summary: Burzum/Aske is a compilation by the Norwegian black metal artist Burzum. It contains Burzum's first two releases: the album Burzum and the mini-album Aske. They were recorded in January 1992 and August 1992, respectively. The cover of this album is the original cover from Burzum's self-titled debut, with the cover art from Aske appearing on the CD artwork. The song A Lost Forgotten Sad Spirit appears on both releases in slightly different versions. On this compilation, only the version from Aske was included. Read more on Last.fm.
